column16: Gerardo Parra singles on a sharp ground ball to right fielder Darin Ruf.   Paul Goldschmidt scores.    Martin Prado scores.    Didi Gregorius to 3rd.
Didi Gregorius walks.   Martin Prado to 2nd.
Martin Prado singles on a line drive to right fielder Darin Ruf.   Adam Eaton scores.    Paul Goldschmidt to 3rd on the throw.
Casper Wells intentionally walks Paul Goldschmidt.
Adam Eaton doubles (4) on a line drive to center fielder Roger Bernadina.   Tony Campana scores.
Tuffy Gosewisch lines out to left fielder John McDonald.
Cliff Pennington grounds out sharply, second baseman Chase Utley to first baseman Michael Young.
Jason Kipnis flies out to left fielder Alejandro De Aza.
Mike Aviles pops out to second baseman Gordon Beckham.
